      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,10 @@\n+# HANSEL Supplement Materials\n+ \n+This repository contains supplementary materials for the user study conducted in the HANSEL project.\n+\n+## Contents\n+ \n+- **prompt.md**: LLM prompts used in the HANSEL pipeline.\n+- **study/User Study Protocol.pdf**: The complete protocol for the user study.\n+- **study/analysis/**: Raw and derived datasets and the Jupyter notebook used for quantitative analysis.\n+- **study/survey/**: Recruitment, pre-study, task response, and post-study surveys."
